description: Redevelopment of Queensland Road North in an amended form to that approved full and outline planning permission under ref. P01/1500 on 30 May 2002.  (The main changes relate to the design of the Plaza building and to the positioning of the permanent access ramps leading to the Emirates Stadium.  Overall, the provision of residential and non-residential accommodation is the same as approved in 2002).
decision_conditions:
CONDITION:  The outline portion of the development hereby permitted shall be begun on or before whichever is the later of the following dates:
i)     3 years from the date of this permission;
ii)    2 years from the final approval of details reserved by this outline permission.

REASON:  To comply with the provisions of Section 92 (4) of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990.
site_name: Queen'S Arms Public House Vacant Land
subdivision_of_building: Land North and South of Queenland Rd.
